# OpenClaw Desktop 🦞

One-click Windows desktop installer for OpenClaw — no command line required.

## 🎯 Problem Solved

- ❌ Complex installation, command line fear
- ❌ Tedious configuration, error-prone
- ❌ Environment issues

**Goal: Make OpenClaw accessible to everyone**

## ✨ Features

### One-Click Installation
- ✅ Automatic environment detection
- ✅ One-click OpenClaw runtime installation
- ✅ Smart configuration wizard

### Model Configuration
- ✅ Support for MiniMax, DeepSeek, Claude and more
- ✅ Visual API Key management
- ✅ One-click connection test

### Channel Integration
- ✅ Feishu Bot configuration
- ✅ Telegram Bot configuration
- ✅ Discord Bot configuration
- ✅ Slack Bot configuration

### System Integration
- ✅ System tray residence
- ✅ Auto-start on boot
- ✅ Minimize to tray

### Monitoring & Operations
- ✅ Gateway status monitoring
- ✅ Real-time log viewing
- ✅ One-click restart

## 📺 Interface Preview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🧠 OpenClaw Desktop               │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│  📊 Status: ✅ Gateway Running     │
│                                     │
│  ⚙️ Model: MiniMax M2.5           │
│  💬 Channel: Feishu               │
│                                     │
│  [Start] [Stop] [Restart]         │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Windows 10/11
- Node.js (v18+) installed

### Installation

1. Download latest release
2. Run installer
3. Enter API Key
4. Select channel (Feishu/Telegram/Discord)
5. Click Start!

